{"tid":1607051,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家行過吉野家 星巴克記得影d食客個狗樣上黎","createTime":"2019-09-30T17:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T12:35:38.000Z","uid":227275,"like":30,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2eae5de89597763240f173e09737a4436e84cf","tid":1607051,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"依家我想發起一個活動 <br />\n首先係 <br />\n食吉野家 死全家<br />\n行過吉野家時大叫 食吉野家 死全家口號<br />\n令到佢地無意欲再幫襯 <br />\n<br />\n第二 每次行過吉野家 星巴克等藍店<br />\n都企係到 影低d食客 嚇下佢地<br />\n夠膽既可以影埋佢地大頭 <br />\n再放上黎依個post <br />\n實行老豆搵仔 搵出平時扮晒黃絲 但又幫襯藍店既仆街<br />\n同時有效阻嚇佢地再幫襯 <br />\n星巴克十個有九個都係打卡放上網死要面既人<br />\n一定唔想比人放上連登"},{"pid":"4f054c798f49bca61f0c0578e7c778a63dddf21f","tid":1607051,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"香城 Online 鍵戰部新職業招募 - 易容師！<br />\n拯救義士 你我有責！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605110</a>"},{"pid":"98220a751f158da7e4e71d68f108e447608996fc","tid":1607051,"uid":201427,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"罷食無得逼<br />\n諗其他方法影響佢生意仲好啦"},{"pid":"38bdeee5ebe95b9b496e769e3385eb1b466b3402","tid":1607051,"uid":202876,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"人地齋坐就唔好影啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b907bbe6834cccec66cb5088470641c5b3ba73d","tid":1607051,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emNRU92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemNRU92.jpg&h=f7d88032&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yi0To3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyi0To3o.jpg&h=7a34a134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日大把後生仔比正價搭黨鐵"},{"pid":"a308702e320f0497a0f12f4d9c181ec93914fca7","tid":1607051,"uid":307619,"like":1,